表格机台休假记录的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('tblMachineVac')
and type = 'U')
drop table tblMachineVac
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: tblMachineVac */
/*==============================================================*/
create table tblMachineVac (
ID int not null,
MachineNo varchar(30) null,
StartDate datetime null,
EndDate datetime null,
Creator varchar(30) null,
CreateDate datetime null,
constraint PK_TBLMACHINEVAC primary key (ID)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'机台休假记录表',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'tblMachineVac'
go
